          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Durable cost $15/month = $45 over 3 months. Mixo cost $9/month = $27 over 3 months. Mixo saved $18. Durable saved 3 minutes of initial setup time.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>Then scenario #2:</strong> A service business needing lead tracking and invoicing. 15 clients, ongoing work, need to manage relationships.</p>
