          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">For the simple landing page, Mixo's $6/month savings adds up over time. For the service business, Durable's CRM saves hours monthly and eliminates $100+/month in tool subscriptions.</p>
          <div class="bg-yellow-100 border-l-[4px] border-yellow-500 p-4 my-4">
